I would like you to turn in the
problem set if you've been

00:00:21.860 --> 00:00:22.785
able to do it.

00:00:22.785 --> 00:00:25.960
If you haven't been able to do
it, that's no great problem,

00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:30.260
but I hope you find
it mildly amusing.

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:33.350
I have given that problem set
out a couple of times over the

00:00:33.350 --> 00:00:39.930
years, and I can recall one very
pale student who appeared

00:00:39.930 --> 00:00:44.400
at my door the next morning
saying it's the first problem

00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:47.380
set, you've only talked an
hour and I can't do it.

