00:05:43.790 --> 00:05:45.380
Woldemar Voigt.

00:05:47.900 --> 00:05:54.060
And the title of this book is
Lehrbuch der Kristallphysik.

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:14.820
And this was published
back in 1910.

00:06:14.820 --> 00:06:16.970
This is the first time
anybody had anything

00:06:16.970 --> 00:06:19.926
to say on the matter.

00:06:19.926 --> 00:06:24.460
It in fact is a big fat book
that contains some topics that

00:06:24.460 --> 00:06:27.030
are not covered in
Wooster and Nye.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:31.940
Nye's book is beautifully
written.

00:06:31.940 --> 00:06:36.410
The first 2/3 of it concerns
tensor formalism and the last

00:06:36.410 --> 00:06:39.580
