00:17:31.430 --> 00:17:34.510
a cube and in the middle of
the faces of the cube.

00:17:34.510 --> 00:17:37.860
If I talk about the arrangement
of sodium ions and

00:17:37.860 --> 00:17:41.930
chlorine ions, that is the
sodium chloride structure and

00:17:41.930 --> 00:17:45.160
not the sodium chloride
lattice.

00:17:45.160 --> 00:17:48.190
And then last time I apologized
for usage so as not

00:17:48.190 --> 00:17:50.160
